div.p:
This then is the distinguishing Character between the Wife Man, & the Fool, & what we may form a Judgment of 'em by; 
                  viz.
                their Closest Application: What is it fixes their Diligence, and commands their Attention? Are they the lower and more trifling Matters that most of all engage 'em? Or, do they keep more noble Ends in their view? steadily pursue what does more nearly concern them, & regard these lesser Matters only by the By?
